  Woodpecker CI

  No native OTEL support yet. The https://www.cncf.io/blog/2024/11/04/opentelemetry-is-expanding-into-ci-cd-observability/ is working on tracing prototypes for CI/CD systems (ArgoCD, GitHub, GitLab, Jenkins), but Woodpecker isn't on that list yet. You'd need to wait for upstream support or contribute a PR.

